1
00:00:00,531 --> 00:00:05,055
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,055 --> 00:00:10,559
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,559 --> 00:00:16,987
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,987 --> 00:00:21,467
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,467 --> 00:00:25,915
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,915 --> 00:00:30,826
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,826 --> 00:00:34,875
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,875 --> 00:00:39,410
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,410 --> 00:00:43,707
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,707 --> 00:00:48,472
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,472 --> 00:00:51,963
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,963 --> 00:00:55,643
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,289 --> 00:01:00,667
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,667 --> 00:01:03,488
=Episode 6=

15
00:01:04,133 --> 00:01:04,933
She is

16
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,096
my secretary,

17
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:09,700
Jin Xi'en.

18
00:01:13,733 --> 00:01:15,099
What's going on?

19
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:16,266
Isn't it Qianqian?

20
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,400
What about Qianqian?

21
00:01:19,433 --> 00:01:21,933
No, that's not true.

22
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:32,866
I'm really not.

23
00:01:32,866 --> 00:01:34,899
Miss Jin, of course you're not.

24
00:01:36,533 --> 00:01:37,933
Who do you think you are?

25
00:01:52,933 --> 00:01:53,866
I'm sorry.

26
00:01:58,233 --> 00:01:59,648
Lan Chen, you are going too far.

27
00:02:00,128 --> 00:02:01,792
Whether now or in the future,

28
00:02:03,433 --> 00:02:05,024
she is my woman.

29
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:09,033
No one can lay a finger on her.

30
00:02:11,733 --> 00:02:12,533
Chen,

31
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,600
what are you saying?

32
00:02:22,816 --> 00:02:25,533
My relationship with Lan Chen
has nothing to do with you.

33
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:29,600
How dare you! No way!

34
00:02:45,984 --> 00:02:47,136
Stop them!

35
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:20,200
Let's go.

36
00:03:54,333 --> 00:03:55,968
When I got outside my house,

37
00:03:56,992 --> 00:03:58,833
he also gave me this.

38
00:03:59,424 --> 00:04:01,333
We have very similar taste.

39
00:04:02,633 --> 00:04:05,100
Now I know why you don't want to quit.

40
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,166
Just now...

41
00:04:41,933 --> 00:04:43,366
I'm working for you,

42
00:04:43,966 --> 00:04:46,200
but I'm not your pawn.

43
00:04:48,766 --> 00:04:49,633
I'm sorry

44
00:04:50,766 --> 00:04:51,799
about what happened.

45
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:55,566
I couldn't think of any other excuse,

46
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,700
so I said it

47
00:04:57,433 --> 00:04:58,833
without considering you.

48
00:04:59,366 --> 00:05:01,200
When have you ever been considerate?

49
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,333
You only think about yourself.

50
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,700
You need company at a banquet,

51
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:07,600
and help with your clothes.

52
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,166
When eating macaron...

53
00:05:09,166 --> 00:05:10,500
Am I so annoying?

54
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:19,000
Yes, you're repugnant.

55
00:05:28,366 --> 00:05:31,333
People who don't know you
would be scared by you.

56
00:05:32,133 --> 00:05:34,766
People who know you
would be angered by you.

57
00:05:35,233 --> 00:05:37,333
You should reflect on yourself.

58
00:05:43,633 --> 00:05:44,433
What about you?

59
00:05:45,433 --> 00:05:46,566
Are you scared

60
00:05:47,566 --> 00:05:48,700
or angered by me?

61
00:05:52,966 --> 00:05:54,766
I just want to beat you.

62
00:05:59,533 --> 00:06:02,666
But this outfit suits you quite well.

63
00:06:12,933 --> 00:06:17,333
I accidentally tore it
when fighting with the security guards.

64
00:06:17,966 --> 00:06:19,264
Is it very expensive?

65
00:06:24,266 --> 00:06:27,433
Can it be deducted from my salary?

66
00:06:36,633 --> 00:06:40,133
Why? It is yours since you've worn it.

67
00:06:40,799 --> 00:06:42,066
Why didn't you tell me?

68
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:44,566
If you had told me,
I'd have been more careful.

69
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,033
It's your fault.

70
00:06:53,900 --> 00:06:54,700
Shooting stars.

71
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,400
Wow,

72
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,533
it's so beautiful.

73
00:07:07,866 --> 00:07:09,133
It's a bit cold.

74
00:07:13,566 --> 00:07:14,699
Yeah, it's chilly.

75
00:07:28,366 --> 00:07:30,000
You have worked hard. Get some rest.

76
00:07:31,733 --> 00:07:32,533
Let's go.

77
00:07:32,966 --> 00:07:36,700
Count this as working overtime.
I'll take the morning off tomorrow.

78
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:39,966
If you dock my pay, you're dead.

79
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,433
I'm sorry.

80
00:07:58,166 --> 00:08:00,499
Miss Gu, I'm really sorry.

81
00:08:01,233 --> 00:08:02,366
I'm sorry.

82
00:08:03,033 --> 00:08:04,266
I'm sorry, Miss Gu.

83
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:07,733
As a mother,
I didn't properly discipline my girl.

84
00:08:07,968 --> 00:08:09,433
You are magnanimous.

85
00:08:10,233 --> 00:08:11,400
Please forgive her.

86
00:08:12,633 --> 00:08:15,500
Ma'am, I understand.

87
00:08:16,366 --> 00:08:21,299
But the financial and moral damage
your daughter has caused us

88
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,333
can't just be ignored like this.

89
00:08:25,633 --> 00:08:29,766
I don't think your family can afford it.

90
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:37,033
Why not sincerely kneel down
and apologize

91
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:42,200
to our two families on her behalf?

92
00:08:42,933 --> 00:08:45,566
Then this matter will be let go, okay?

93
00:08:46,066 --> 00:08:47,499
Miss Gu,

94
00:08:47,533 --> 00:08:51,133
it has nothing to do with my mother.
Please don't make it hard for her.

95
00:08:52,466 --> 00:08:54,528
Are you schizophrenic?

96
00:08:56,166 --> 00:08:59,733
You were so arrogant just now,
and now you're backing down.

97
00:09:01,933 --> 00:09:05,099
Your mother didn't teach you
to be responsible for your behaviors.

98
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:06,560
Today, I'll teach you.

99
00:09:10,963 --> 00:09:15,485
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

100
00:09:18,515 --> 00:09:23,476
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

101
00:09:26,525 --> 00:09:32,349
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

102
00:09:32,349 --> 00:09:38,848
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

103
00:09:39,819 --> 00:09:43,300
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

104
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:47,421
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

105
00:09:47,421 --> 00:09:49,117
♪Open my secret♪

106
00:09:49,117 --> 00:09:55,165
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

107
00:09:55,165 --> 00:09:59,037
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

108
00:09:59,037 --> 00:10:03,543
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

109
00:10:05,472 --> 00:10:12,253
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
